## Tooling (Python)

- `uv sync` тАФ install deps ┬╖ `uv add <pkg>` тАФ add a dep
- `uv run pytest` тАФ tests ┬╖ `uv run ruff check . && uv run ruff format .` тАФ lint + format
- CI gates **diff coverage**: 100% of changed lines, via `diff-cover` over `pytest --cov`.
- Layout: `src/{{ module_name }}/`, tests in `tests/`. Python >= {{ python_version }}.
